superabundant,
or

too

dear.

been

the
due
proportion
between
people

and
land
may

constantly
secured

abandon-

ing
the

grants,

an

uniform

out
exception. '
If

too
low,

deters
"speculators

view

injurious
dispersion ;

the
only
means
of

supply
of
labour
for
hire.
If,

other
hand,
.the

narrow,

thrifty

sufficient,
